{"tid":1757883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依家我地絕對需要keep住搞和理非活動 俾勇武休息","createTime":"2019-11-26T17:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T18:32:51.000Z","uid":306058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9eb39b2820c6de064769ebb23380afe601755dc","tid":1757883,"uid":306058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:56:08.000Z","msg":"我知好多手足都有搞緊和理非活動 入緊紙<br />\n好多謝你地嘅付出<br />\n我所講嘅「俾勇武休息」<br />\n係因為勇武係中大 理大都元氣大傷<br />\n相信大家都明<br />\n同埋最精銳嘅勇武係愈黎愈少(因為受傷/被捕等等)<br />\n依家場上好多都係新手(我都係最近先開始發夢)<br />\n我地好需要磨練<br />\n同時俾時間勇武抖同埋新手進化<br />\n區選啱啱完<br />\n係我地清晰地用最和理非嘅方式表達自己嘅政見/立場<br />\n依家係最好嘅時機重新再搞和理非活動<br />\n因為區選證明咗我地唔會同勇武/所謂「暴力」割蓆<br />\n同時可以設下死線 逼正苦回應<br />\n和理非&gt;勇武&gt;和理非&gt;勇武<br />\n繼續呢條方程式<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港時化革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n香港人 報仇"},{"pid":"e7de508ce1b4a47793cf028f288004241e144c3a","tid":1757883,"uid":299490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:58:12.000Z","msg":"「文宣」最新香港人日程表!!!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757860</a>"},{"pid":"8cce61030a6919b146231e21811a05b9b0ca2b13","tid":1757883,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acab26fb3e6e31dc5425e5d97550b6c6ddad910b","tid":1757883,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，<br />\n以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1756593/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQj1KLO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQj1KLO.jpg&h=ed72b375&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb67daad69cd3822f45a408c58fd0e717b486b76","tid":1757883,"uid":143319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:32:51.000Z